# Project Structure Guide

This project is structured as follows:

- **Configuration & CI**
  - [build.gradle](mdc:build.gradle): Gradle build script
  - [settings.gradle](mdc:settings.gradle): Gradle settings
  - [gradlew](mdc:gradlew) / [gradlew.bat](mdc:gradlew.bat): Gradle wrapper scripts
  - [\.github/](mdc:.github): CI workflows and issue templates

- **Build & Caches**
  - [.gradle/](mdc:.gradle): Gradle cache directory
  - [build/](mdc:build): Gradle build outputs

- **Core Source Code**
  - [src/main/kotlin/net/ccbluex/liquidbounce](mdc:src/main/kotlin/net/ccbluex/liquidbounce): Main Kotlin source root
    - [api/](mdc:src/main/kotlin/net/ccbluex/liquidbounce/api): Public API definitions
    - [config/](mdc:src/main/kotlin/net/ccbluex/liquidbounce/config): Configuration management
    - [event/](mdc:src/main/kotlin/net/ccbluex/liquidbounce/event): Event system
    - [features/](mdc:src/main/kotlin/net/ccbluex/liquidbounce/features): Modules, commands, and chat features
    - [render/](mdc:src/main/kotlin/net/ccbluex/liquidbounce/render): Rendering engine and shaders
    - [utils/](mdc:src/main/kotlin/net/ccbluex/liquidbounce/utils): Utility functions and helpers
  - [src/main/resources](mdc:src/main/resources): Resource files (assets, data, language files, shaders)

- **Web UI (Theme)**
  - [src-theme/src](mdc:src-theme/src): Frontend source (React/TypeScript) for click GUI, HUD, menus
  - [src-theme/resources](mdc:src-theme/resources): Static assets for the theme
  - [src-theme/dist](mdc:src-theme/dist): Compiled assets for distribution

- **Tests & Validation**
  - [src/test/kotlin](mdc:src/test/kotlin): Unit tests for core functionality
  - [build/reports](mdc:build/reports): Test and static analysis reports

- **Documentation & Memory**
  - [README.md](mdc:README.md): Project overview
  - [Memory.md](mdc:Memory.md): AI assistant memory and ongoing roadmap

Use these anchors when navigating the codebase. Each section corresponds to a major component or workflow.
